### 📋 **API 통합 스펙 APPROVED**

#### **Cursor API 호출 방식:**
```javascript
// ClaudeCode에서 Cursor 호출
const response = await fetch('http://localhost:3000/api/social/extract', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify({ 
    url: "https://www.instagram.com/p/ABC123/",
    platform: "instagram",
    options: { download_video: true, extract_comments: true }
  })
});
```

#### **Response 변환 로직:**
```javascript
// Cursor 응답 → VDP 형식 변환
function convertCursorToVDP(cursorData) {
  return {
    content_key: `${cursorData.platform}:${cursorData.data.content_id}`,
    content_id: cursorData.data.content_id,
    metadata: {
      platform: cursorData.platform,
      view_count: cursorData.data.metadata.view_count,
      like_count: cursorData.data.metadata.like_count,
      comment_count: cursorData.data.metadata.comment_count,
      top_comments: cursorData.data.metadata.top_comments,
      // ... VDP 필수 필드들
    }
  };
}
```

